title: 93: The Walmart Haul Episode (March 2020 Edition)
itunes:title: The Walmart Haul Episode (March 2020 Edition)
description: In today’s episode, Lisa, Mikey, and Jamie are taste-testing healthy products like vegan sliders, Instant Pot chicken stew, pasta sauce, kraut, chili, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, we debut a new feature called “Can You Believe This Really Exists?” And sadly, the product was a MAJOR DUD! So, wait no more… Push play, and when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the products and their ratings!
itunes:summary: We went back to Walmart, and boy, did we find a lot of WINNERS!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
